This is an intense psychological thriller that kept me riveted. Nick Dunne and Amy Eliot Dunne initially seem like the perfect couple, but eventually, as the story unfolds, cracks in their relationship begin to appear. When Amy goes missing, the lives of all of those around her would be impacted, particularly Nick. I do not wish to go into further detail (I would be giving away spoilers!), but suffice to say, a fantastic read.
