Excellent character sketches of a deceptive wife and her equally deceptive husband. In a story that reads like a cat and mouse game, we are exposed layer by layer to a decaying relationship, and the lengths to which lies are told in the name of self-preservation.Overall, a cunning tale with fast, economical, and sometimes clipped writing.
