I am not one to just read any book. I choose thoughtfully. This book was an excellent choice. It only took me 3 days to read the book. I did not want to put it down. There were a few parts I found a bit dry, and sluggish. However, those parts made sense in the end and in the development of each person. I found my self hating Amy, then feeling sorry for her, and then back to hating her. With Nick, I felt sorry for him a lot, then to pure disgust, and on to pity. They are both quite awful people and once their stories open fully you are shocked at the vile qualities in both of them. Unfortunately, I know a few people in my own life that are about as awful as these two. That fact made this story quite hard to read and at the same time, left me wanting to go further.Some people have complained the language is awful, but honestly, from two horrible character what else would you expect? I think it was wrote brilliantly, language and all. I also am not sure what others were complaining about such graphic sex? What one or maybe two scenes? That wasn't graphic!!!
