This was the first book I read from Gillian Flynn but it won't be my last. I read a lot of books and typically I finish a book this size in roughly 3 days of sporadic reading. This book took longer. The first part was a slow build. In fact, I am impressed that she held my attention so well considering the pace of the read. But that goes to the quality of the writing. By the second part of the book, it began to move fast. I couldn't put the book down by the end.The story itself was great... Really exciting to read and the plot kept me entertained and interested.  I would absolutely recommend this book to anyone looking for a great thought-provoking book that also happens to be very intelligent and well written.
