If you have ever met a couple that were so devastatingly awful for each other, that you couldn't understand why they would stay together, then this book is for you.  A psychological thriller that starts off slow and sullen before it calmly begins to curve into a twist.  Then it picks up speed, hugging the turns, and weaving faster and faster until it smashes, head-on into an unimaginable ending.  You will walk away shaken, confused, and yet somehow completely agree with everything that just occurred.
