This book is a true page turner. From beginning to end you want to know what really happened. It starts with a love story, dating, engagement and marriage. Then the wife turns up missing and clues lead the authorities to believe it was murder by the husband. Yet as you read from the husband's point of view you realize that it doesn't fit together. You cling to the book trying to figure out what really happenedThe movie is just as amazing as the book but beware, it'll spoil the ending.
