The book is written by 2 points of view:  both the husband and wife.  The author goes back and forth between the 2, while they tell the story.  Which, keeps the reader continually wondering what happens next, but has to get through another chapter just to get to that part, and the cycle begins.  Basically, this book is hard to put down.  Lots of twists and turns.  Just when you're loving/siding with one character, you find something new about another.  Very well written book.  Great read!
