Cleverly written with alternating chapters from the viewpoint of the main characters, husband, Nick, and wife, Amy, the story unfolds so gently that one would never suspect the anger and viciousness that increases in intensity with each page. The author has brilliantly constructed a complex tale that seems unbelievable and yet very believable all at the same time. Warning: You will not be able to put this book down once you start it.
