This is an amazing tale of two people dealing with all the baggage that can be thought of. You find your emotions swinging between rooting for and strongly disliking both Nick & Amy. If you are married or in a committed relationship of any kind, all the feelings they have for each other will be familiar. The writer does an excellent job writing both points of view. Read this book!!!
