This intricately plotted novel begins as a compelling read and becomes downright compulsive. The ending strains plausibility but is no less enjoyable and satisfying. It is, like its title character, dazzling and clever and fluid in its assumptions. Its masterful use of the unreliable narrator should be studied in writing workshops.
