This is a very well written book about two rancid people, bothof whom are total phonies. It is a testament to the author's skillthat she has made such lowlifes interesting. A deep dive into crazy.Doubtless it will be a movie  Nick-Ryan Gosling  Amy-  Amy Adams  Margo the sister- emma stone  Det. Boney  Clair Danes  Tanner Bolt the lawyer- John Slattery  Nancy Grace playing herself  Desi- Esai Morales  Susan Scheiber- Maggie Gylenhaal  Desi's mother-Glenn Close  Amy's parent- Ted Danson and Mary Steenbergen
